summary:
I am a persevering, proactive and tidy individual. Resourceful and
quick when it comes to solving problems. Also always open receptive
to feedback and on a constant journey of improvement. A team
player with commitment, humility, companionship and sincerity as
core values. Those who know me say that I am the kind of leader who
says "let's go" instead of "go". Dynamism is my way to go when it
comes to teamwork and team building. Moreover I believe working
outside ones comfort brings out the best in people and teams, which
leads to a motivated group and a sense of teamwork in work
environments.
